snippet.title: Is This Farming Game My New OBSESSION? | Cornucopia First Look
snippet.description:
Playing the demo of this 2.5D farming sim was some of the most fun I had in a farming game other than Stardew Valley in a while. Cornucopia has a fantastic art style and looks to be rich and filled with lots of things to do.

I was sent this game to show it off, and I'm so excited to do that today! 

Cornucopia is out for Early Access on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1681600/Cornucopia/

Cornucopia - an immersive 2.5D farming sim with 50+ NPCs, innovative compost system, unique card system, 200+ recipes. Befriend, date, marry, and have children with 31 NPCs. Attend festivals, auction animals, fish, craft, and play mini-games. In-depth gardening, pet-assisted interactions, and more!

STREAM SCHEDULE:
Fridays and Sundays at 11AM PST

CHAT RULES:
∘Keep it a PG-13 family-friendly
∘No self-promo or spamming
∘English only, please
∘Be excellent to each other and help each other out
∘Keep the convo light and friendly
∘Dad Jokes welcome
